{"article_id":"JoUxBhqOH2hwwOQQ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A new piece of evidence has emerged","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"buttressing the credibility of Tara Reade ' s claim","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"that she told her mother about allegations of sexual harassment and assault","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"related to her former boss , then-Sen. Joe Biden .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Biden , through a spokesperson , has denied the allegations .","depth":2},{"id":5,"text":"Reade has claimed to various media outlets ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"including ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that she told her mother , a close friend , and her brother about both the harassment and , to varying degrees of detail , the assault at the time .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Her brother , Collin Moulton , and her friend ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"who has asked to remain anonymous ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"both confirmed","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that they heard about the allegations from Reade at the time .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Reade ' s mother died in 2016 ,","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"but both her brother and friend also confirmed","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Reade had told her mother ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and that her mother , a longtime feminist and activist , urged her to go to the police .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"In interviews with , Reade also mentioned","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that her mother had made a phone call to \" Larry King Live \" on CNN ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"during which she made reference to her daughter ' s experience on Capitol Hill .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Reade told","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"that her mother called in","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"asking for advice","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"after Reade , then in her 20s , left Biden ' s office .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"\" I remember","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"it being an anonymous call","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"and her saying","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"my daughter was sexually harassed and retaliated against and fired ,","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"where can she go for help ?","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"I was mortified , \"","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Reade told me .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Reade couldn ' t remember the date or the year of the phone call ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"and King didn ' t include the names of callers on his show .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"I was unable to find the call ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"but mentioned it in an interview with Katie Halper , the podcast host","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"who first aired Reade ' s allegation .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"After the podcast aired ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"a listener managed to find the call","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and sent it to .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"On August 11 , 1993 , King aired a program","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"titled , \" Washington : The Cruelest City on Earth ? \"","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"Toward the end of the program , he introduces a caller","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"dialing in from San Luis Obispo , California .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Congressional records list August 1993 as Reade ' s last month of employment with Biden ' s Senate office ,","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"and ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"according to property records ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Reade ' s mother , Jeanette Altimus , was living in San Luis Obispo County .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Here is the transcript of the beginning of the call :","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"KING :","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"San Luis Obispo , California , hello .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"CALLER :","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Yes , hello .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"I ' m wondering what a staffer would do","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"besides go to the press in Washington ?","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"My daughter has just left there ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"after working for a prominent senator ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"and could not get through with her problems at all ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"and the only thing","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"she could have done","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"was go to the press ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"and she chose not to do it out of respect for him .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"KING :","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"In other words , she had a story","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"to tell","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"but , out of respect for the person","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"she worked for , she didn ' t tell it ?","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"CALLER :","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"That ' s true .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"King ' s panel of guests offered no suggestions ,","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"and instead the conversation veered into a discussion","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"of whether any of the men on set would leak damaging personal information about a rival to the press .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"Reade ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"after being read the transcript of the call ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that it gelled with her memory of it ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"and ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"after the video was surfaced ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"confirmed","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"it is her mother ' s voice on the call .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"\" Aww , I have not heard my mom ' s voice in awhile , \"","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"There are several notable things about the emergence of the call .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"On the one hand , the caller does not specifically mention \" sexual harassment \" or retaliation ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"as Reade had recalled .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"On the other hand , the reference","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to being unable to \" get through with her problems \" aligns with Reade ' s claim","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that she complained to superiors in Biden ' s office","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"and got nowhere ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"and the reference","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"to going to the press","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"makes clear that the caller is talking about more than just generic problems at the office .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"The problems ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"she makes clear ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"would damage the senator","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"if exposed .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Reade ' s inability","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"to remember the exact date of the alleged assault , or its precise location , or the precise location of the office","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"where she picked up the form","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"needed","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"to file a complaint ,","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"has been used by skeptics","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"to suggest","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"the allegation is fabricated .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"What the emergence of the call shows is that","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"even if Reade ' s memory is off on timing or details ,","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"the substance of her claims","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"- in this case , that her mother called Larry King","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"and discussed her situation -","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"can still be true .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"The call also calls into question the credibility of Biden ' s denial .","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"Reade said","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"that she filed a complaint about Biden ' s harassment with Marianne Baker , effectively the office manager in the Biden office .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"The Biden campaign released a statement from Baker ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"which said","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"that neither Reade nor any other employee had ever complained about improper behavior .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"\" In all my years","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"working for Senator Biden ,","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"I never once witnessed , or heard of , or received , any reports of inappropriate conduct , period","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"- not from Ms. Reade , not from anyone , \"","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"Baker said in the campaign ' s statement .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"\" These clearly false allegations are in complete contradiction to both the inner workings of our Senate office and to the man","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"I know","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"and worked so closely with for almost two decades. \"","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"For Baker ' s statement to be true ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"Reade would have had to have lied to her friend , brother , and mother about having complained to Biden ' s office .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"There is no obvious reason","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"Reade would make up a story to those closest to her about the Senate office not taking Biden ' s harassment seriously ,","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"while at the same time resisting pressure","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"to go to the press .","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"Reade has said","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"that the complaint","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"she filed","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"was related to the harassment","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"she said","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"she faced ,","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"and did not address the assault .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"The complaint was left with Biden ' s office ,","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"if it still exists ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"is with Biden ' s papers at the University of Delaware .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"The school recently told reporter Rich McHugh","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"that the papers are sealed until two years after Biden leaves public life .","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"And @ UDelaware","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"-- which houses the collection of Joe Biden 's senatorial papers --","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"just confirmed to me","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"that the papers `` will remain closed to the public until two years","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"after Mr. Biden retires from public life . ''","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"- Rich McHugh","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"( @ RichMcHugh )","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"April 21 , 2020","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":297,"left":153,"right":296,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":0,"right":151,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":1,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":193,"right":295,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":193,"left":163,"right":192,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":163,"left":159,"right":162,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":155,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":154,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":157,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":156,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":156,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":12,"right":161,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":161,"left":13,"right":160,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":160,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":192,"left":186,"right":191,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":184,"right":185,"relation":"context","nuclearity